      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――劇団★見、舞台本番",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Troupe★Hoshimi‚ On Stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "私はすずアリスですわ！　さあ、外で遊びますわよ！\n……あら？　あれは何かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am Suzu Alice! Come now‚ let’s play outside!\n…Oh? What might that be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5333333731,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.3332936,
          "startTime": 7.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13566.6666667,
          "startTime": 23.1000000398
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_poi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3046.7578252000003,
          "startTime": 12.5800911983
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_poi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3046.7578252000003,
          "startTime": 12.5800911983
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_poi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3046.7578252000003,
          "startTime": 12.5800911983
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_poi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3046.7578252000003,
          "startTime": 12.5800911983
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "うさぎが穴に飛び込みましたわ！　これは大冒険の\n予感がしますわね。私達も追いかけますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rabbit jumped into the hole! This feels like the start\nof a grand adventure. Let’s chase after it too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5333328645,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12533.3338022,
          "startTime": 31.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "雫アリスとはぐれてしまいましたわ……\n一体どこに行って……あら？　木の上に何かいますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve gotten separated from Shizuku Alice…\nWhere could she be… oh? There’s something up in that tree.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333323558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（おお……思わず見入ってしまうな）\n（やるじゃないか、すず）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Whoa… I can’t help but be drawn in.）\n（You’re doing great‚ Suzu.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3021.0427999999965,
          "startTime": 43.9877094667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.73
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9877094667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、観てくださいましたか！\nこの大女優、成宮すずの完璧なアリスを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ did you see it!?\nThe perfect Alice performed by the great actress‚ Suzu Narumiya!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.177300493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に素晴らしかったぞ\nほら、ご両親も感動してまだ泣いているぐらいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was truly wonderful.\nLook‚ even your parents are so moved they’re still crying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.7565478405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、お父様とお母様ったら……ふふふ\nもっともっと褒めてくださってもいいんですのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ Father and Mother… fufufu.\nYou know‚ you may praise me even more if you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0572953304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.2128726404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "「すずのアリス役が観れて本当に嬉しい」？　私も\nですわ！　今回やっとアリスを演じられたんですもの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“We’re so happy we got to see Suzu play Alice”? I feel the same!\nAfter all‚ this time I finally got to play Alice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5572943132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ……すず？\nやっとアリス役を演じられた……？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a second… Suzu?\nYou finally got to play Alice…? What do you mean by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9355257115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "しまっ……わ、私としたことが……！\n違いますの、これはその、ご、誤解ですの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no… h-how careless of me…!\nThat’s not it‚ this is‚ um‚ a misunderstanding…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2572951079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　お父さん、お母さんどうしました？\n「この映像を観れば分かる」……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Father‚ Mother‚ what is it?\n“You’ll understand if you watch this video”…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2362056177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "んなぁ！？　そっ、それは、この間隠し通したはずの\n昔のアリスの劇！　スマホにも保存してたんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha—!? Th-that’s the old Alice play\nI thought I’d hidden! You even saved it on your phone!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9473649929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "一体いくつ予備があるんですの！？　ちょ、待って\nくださいまし、再生しないでくださいまし～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just how many copies do you have!?\nP-please wait— please don’t play it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4835955064,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7971.852771400009,
          "startTime": 127.0666717529
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7287030936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こ、この映像は……！　……と、とりあえず\nすずと話してもよろしいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this video is…! …F-for now‚\nmay I have a word with Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0053608339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "もう言い逃れは……\nどうやっても出来なそうですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no more room for excuses…\nNo matter what I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8935926835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2811944247
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2811944247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ混乱しているんだが\nあの映像について説明してくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m still confused‚\ncan you explain that video to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.7729640086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "見ていただいた通りですわ……実は、私……\nアリスの役なんてやったことなかったんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as you saw… the truth is‚ I…\nhad never played the role of Alice before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7729640086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "私は、その……雫と同じで、木の役しか演じたことが\nなかったんですの……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ um… just like Shizuku‚ I had only ever played\nthe role of a tree…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2729640086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.9951608896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……\n今までの妙な態度が腑に落ちたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nNow your strange behavior makes sense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "申し訳ありません、{user}さん……\n騙すつもりはなかったんですの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m very sorry‚ {user}-san…\nI never intended to deceive you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.1396336794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.9586525995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かっているさ、勘違いしていた俺も悪かった\nでも……どうして黙っていたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. I was at fault too for misunderstanding.\nBut… why did you keep it a secret?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "その……さっきの木の役を演じた映像の中で\nお父様とお母様、私を褒めちぎっていたでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… in that video where I played the tree‚\nFather and Mother were praising me so much‚ weren’t they?",
