      "text": "ですが、私には心強い声援でも、同級生からは嘲笑の的\nでしたの。劇が終わった後、酷くからかわれてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But while it was encouraging to me‚ I became a target of ridicule\namong my classmates. After the play ended‚ they teased me terribly.",
